&#039;Pretty Odd&#039; is the second album from American outfit Panic At The Disco. Recorded 
in their hometown Las Vegas with pop producer Rob Mathes (Carly Simon, Vanessa Williams)
 the album sees PATD continue with the emo inspired indie rock that graced their debut
 and earned them three UK Top 40 hits. The singles &#039;Nine In The Afternoon&#039; and &#039;That Green
 Gentleman&#039; are included.
